how to get what is eating your hard disk  
du -h -t 1G | sort -h  
how to fix database logs .bin error  
located at /var/lib/mysql   

read more about  this comand

PURGE BINARY LOGS TO `mysql-bin.000014`;

https://dba.stackexchange.com/questions/41050/is-it-safe-to-delete-mysql-bin-files


then add this to /etc/my.cnf   

[mysqld]   
expire_logs_days=3
